name: 5 x 1k
desc: 1 mile warm-up followed by 5 reps of 1k with 90 seconds easy jogging in between reps. Finish with 1 mile cool down.

name: 3 x 1k
desc: 1 mile warm-up followed by 3 reps of 1k with 2 minutes easy jogging in between reps. Finish with 1 mile cool down.

name: 4 x 800, 4 x 400, 4 x 100
desc: 1 mile warm-up followd by 4 reps of 800m with 90 seconds easy jogging in between. Then 4 reps of 400m with 90 seconds easy jogging in between. Finally, 4 reps of 100m with 90 seconds easy jogging in between. Finish with 1 mile cool down.
pace: 800s at 10k pace, 400s at 5k pace, 100s at full effort

name: 3 x 800, 3 x 400
desc: 1 mile warm-up followd by 3 reps of 800m with 2 minutes easy jogging in between. Then 3 reps of 400m with 90 seconds easy jogging in between. Finish with 1 mile cool down.
pace: 800s at 10k pace, 400s at 5k pace, 100s at full effort

name: Mile Cutdown
desc: 1 mile warm-up followed by 1 rep of 1 mile with 90 second jog rest, 2 reps of 800m with 60 sec jog rest after each, 4 reps of 400m with 45 second jog rest after each, and 8 reps of 200m with 30 second jog rest after each. Finish with 1 mile cool down
pace: 1 mile at 10k pace, 800s at 5k pace, 400s at 3k pace, 100s at 1 mile pace

name: Mile Cutdown
desc: 1 mile warm-up followed by 1 rep of 1 mile with 90 second jog rest, 2 reps of 800m with 60 sec jog rest after each, 4 reps of 400m with 45 second jog rest after each. Finish with 1 mile cool down
pace: 1 mile at 10k pace, 800s at 5k pace, 400s at 3k pace, 100s at 1 mile pace
